-- South Korea to Vaccinate Animals to Prevent Foot-and-Mouth Disease Spread
-- B y   S h i n h y e   K a n g
-- 2010-12-22T22:04:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-22/south-korea-to-vaccinate-animals-to-prevent-foot-and-mouth-disease-spread.html
South Korean government will
vaccinate animals to prevent the spread of foot-and-mouth
disease, the agriculture ministry said late yesterday on its
website. Timing and target of the vaccination will be decided
later, according to the ministry.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Shinhye Kang in Seoul at 
 skang24@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
